{"tid":2221552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有黑警衝入太古廣場拉十幾歲細路","createTime":"2020-09-28T12:41:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T00:47:14.000Z","uid":188515,"like":412,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"4e56673c09ca601771b549f87820df8d88c5acbf","tid":2221552,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:41:46.000Z","msg":"2014年，港人為爭取「真普選」發起歷時79天的「雨傘運動」，佔領中環、旺角及銅鑼灣的主要道路，要求中央及香港政府回應訴求，惜最終以清場落幕，社運氣氛一度低沉。惟去年港府硬推「送中惡法」，再次激起港人怒憤，爆發「反送中」運動，社運人士更吸取「雨傘運動」教訓，提出「和勇不分」、「無大台」等流水式抗爭策略。6年前的今天，第一顆催淚彈落下夏慤道；6年後的今天，爭取民主的港人再重聚，盼「念念不忘，必有迴響」。<br />\n<br />\n網民今晚（28日）在金鐘太古廣場發起「和你Shop」行動，紀念傘運6周年。經常響應「和你Lunch」行動、人稱「Lunch哥」的David亦有現身，惟在商場唱出半首《願榮光歸香港》時，警即闖入商場驅趕，並在2樓帶走一名10多歲男童上警車。<br />\n<br />\n傘運6周年Lunch哥唱半首《榮光》 警即闖太古廣場驅趕 帶走10多歲男童<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200928/QCUHVTPFLBHADHXZI5USV7RYQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200928%2FQCUHVTPFLBHADHXZI5USV7RYQY%2F&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=110c6171\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200928%2FQCUHVTPFLBHADHXZI5USV7RYQY%2F&h=88c0ce42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200928/QCUHVTPFLBHADHXZI5USV7RYQY/</a>"},{"pid":"02eb5155b234f4a0fc0f9b5e22519eafc4406810","tid":2221552,"uid":188515,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:42:13.000Z","msg":"順道一推。10月1日見<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/B5PH7XlgFWc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB5PH7XlgFWc&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=ee3c9ac5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B5PH7XlgFWc</a>"},{"pid":"5115b0a3b1e60e80c89caa6ff593ffcbfff973df","tid":2221552,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/an